"title": "7520: dispersion, the",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7520: dispersion, the",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A technical term used to refer to God's people as they are scattered throughout the world.</p>\n<h2>The dispersion of the Jews</h2>\n<h3>Promised and predicted</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:25-Deut4:28\">DEU 4:25–4:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:15\">1KI 14:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:15-Deut28:68\">DEU 28:15–28:68</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:27-Lev26:35\">LEV 26:27–26:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:8-Neh1:9\">NEH 1:8–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:24\">JER 13:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:8-Ezek6:10\">EZK 6:8–6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:23-Ezek20:24\">EZK 20:23–20:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:15\">EZK 22:15</a></p>\n<h3>The prediction fulfilled</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:17\">JER 50:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:7\">DAN 9:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:8\">EST 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:9-Ps44:16\">PSA 44:9–44:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:16\">LAM 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:17-Ezek36:20\">EZK 36:17–36:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:10\">ZEP 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:19\">ZEC 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:35\">JHN 7:35</a> <em>In NT times there were more Jews living outside Palestine than within.</em></p>\n<h3>The promise of return</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:12\">ISA 11:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:29-Deut4:31\">DEU 4:29–4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:10\">JER 31:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:16-Ezek11:17\">EZK 11:16–11:17</a></p>\n<h2>The dispersion of Christians</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:1\">ACT 8:1</a></strong> <em>Christians scattered because of persecution</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:1\">1PE 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:4\">ACT 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:19\">ACT 11:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:1\">JAS 1:1</a></p>",
